How to Install phonegap-plugin-menu
===================================

Copy Files
----------

Copy all files except `INSTALL` to your Android project.
The directory structure of the files is important.

Update plugins.xml
------------------

Add the following four elements to `res/xml/plugins.xml`:

    <plugin name="com.phonegap.menu.toolbar"         value="com.phonegap.menu.AppMenu" />
    <plugin name="com.phonegap.menu.toolbar.command" value="com.phonegap.menu.AppMenuItem" />
    <plugin name="com.phonegap.menu.context"         value="com.phonegap.menu.AppMenu" />
    <plugin name="com.phonegap.menu.context.command" value="com.phonegap.menu.AppMenuItem" />
